        "subject": "LU-2744 build: fix race issues thanks to oap_lock",
        "message": "LU-2744 build: fix race issues thanks to oap_lock\n\nFix 'data race condition' defects found by Coverity version\n6.5.0:\nData race condition (MISSING_LOCK)\nAccessing variable without holding lock. Elsewhere,\nthis variable is accessed with lock held.\n\nThis patch is dedicated to code fragments involving oap_lock.\n\nSigned-off-by: Sebastien Buisson <sebastien.buisson@bull.net>\nChange-Id: Ibe03e3e57efc9b4a0976863645b376c9679dfd10\n"
      },
